<h1>About Shine Get</h1>

<p>Shine get is a wish list aggregator - it allows you to make your own wish list
  or to load wish lists you have created elsewhere on the internet.</p>
<p>Each item you have in your wish list will be monitored for price changes so you can
  come back and see which of your desired items are currently on sale or at a lower price!</p>

<p>There's more info to follow, but for now why not check out the
  <a href="https://github.com/ajwillia-ms/shineget" target="_blank">project page</a>.</p>